{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/posts/develop-tool-part1/","webpackCompilationHash":"ae0b49e940e93fca6483","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"a970c504-e5b5-587c-98bd-7005741126d4","html":"<p><strong>簡單介紹一下自己用到或看到覺得好用的開發工具，這篇分享一下 code sharing 的工具</strong></p>\n<p>在 demo 自己實作的程式時，常常需要分享寫出來的 code，但在製作投影片時，不像網頁或是文字編輯器的環境，有 syntax highlight 的幫忙，只能貼上跑版的純文字來炸別人眼睛，或是擷取文字編輯器的畫面。這些做法不是麻煩，就是不美觀。所以就找了幾個好用的工具來幫忙處理這些瑣事。</p>\n<h3 id=\"1-carbon\"><a href=\"#1-carbon\" aria-label=\"1 carbon permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><a href=\"https://carbon.now.sh/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">1. Carbon</a></h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 960px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 43.99999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/d485ae8f1ed788332bc2e1970c3866dd/01472/carbon.webp 240w,\n/static/d485ae8f1ed788332bc2e1970c3866dd/222bd/carbon.webp 480w,\n/static/d485ae8f1ed788332bc2e1970c3866dd/620b9/carbon.webp 960w,\n/static/d485ae8f1ed788332bc2e1970c3866dd/28063/carbon.webp 1440w,\n/static/d485ae8f1ed788332bc2e1970c3866dd/5ea2f/carbon.webp 1750w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/d485ae8f1ed788332bc2e1970c3866dd/0783d/carbon.png 240w,\n/static/d485ae8f1ed788332bc2e1970c3866dd/782f4/carbon.png 480w,\n/static/d485ae8f1ed788332bc2e1970c3866dd/f570d/carbon.png 960w,\n/static/d485ae8f1ed788332bc2e1970c3866dd/8d0ff/carbon.png 1440w,\n/static/d485ae8f1ed788332bc2e1970c3866dd/da2f0/carbon.png 1750w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n          type=\"image/png\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/d485ae8f1ed788332bc2e1970c3866dd/f570d/carbon.png\"\n          alt=\"carbon photo\"\n          title=\"carbon photo\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n    </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: -20px;\">\n  (image from <a href=\"https://carbon.now.sh/\">carbon</a>)\n</p>\n<p>Carbon 可以把你的 code 轉成 png、svg，還可以建立 url，甚至 embed 進網頁。</p>\n<p>使用方法就是點進網頁後把要分享的 code 貼上去，並調整成想要的樣式，之後 export 就可以選擇格式輸出。</p>\n<h3 id=\"2-polacode\"><a href=\"#2-polacode\" aria-label=\"2 polacode permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><a href=\"https://github.com/octref/polacode\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">2. Polacode</a></h3>\n<p><img src=\"/b2f6a95ac83c04379158cbbb131c52fc/polacode.gif\" alt=\"polacode photo\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: -20px;\">\n  (image from <a href=\"https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=pnp.polacode\">polacode</a>)\n</p>\n<p>Polacode 是 VSCode 的一個 extension，可以說是 Carbon 的延伸版，Polacode 的作者也說他受 Carbon 啟發。</p>\n<p>功能上比 Carbon 更好用，是直接從文字編輯器輸出，可以直接拖拉改變輸出樣式。如果平常就是使用 VSCode 的話，十分建議安裝使用。</p>\n<h3 id=\"3-revealjs\"><a href=\"#3-revealjs\" aria-label=\"3 revealjs permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><a href=\"https://revealjs.com/#/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">3. reveal.js</a></h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 960px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 53.06406685236769%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/4773115a502cbc7a336254d3daaa1f72/01472/revealjs.webp 240w,\n/static/4773115a502cbc7a336254d3daaa1f72/222bd/revealjs.webp 480w,\n/static/4773115a502cbc7a336254d3daaa1f72/620b9/revealjs.webp 960w,\n/static/4773115a502cbc7a336254d3daaa1f72/28063/revealjs.webp 1440w,\n/static/4773115a502cbc7a336254d3daaa1f72/34ef4/revealjs.webp 1920w,\n/static/4773115a502cbc7a336254d3daaa1f72/c9a76/revealjs.webp 2872w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/4773115a502cbc7a336254d3daaa1f72/0783d/revealjs.png 240w,\n/static/4773115a502cbc7a336254d3daaa1f72/782f4/revealjs.png 480w,\n/static/4773115a502cbc7a336254d3daaa1f72/f570d/revealjs.png 960w,\n/static/4773115a502cbc7a336254d3daaa1f72/8d0ff/revealjs.png 1440w,\n/static/4773115a502cbc7a336254d3daaa1f72/a987b/revealjs.png 1920w,\n/static/4773115a502cbc7a336254d3daaa1f72/97d83/revealjs.png 2872w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n          type=\"image/png\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/4773115a502cbc7a336254d3daaa1f72/f570d/revealjs.png\"\n          alt=\"revealjs photo\"\n          title=\"revealjs photo\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Reveal.js 是提供網頁製作投影片的 Framework。以網頁為基礎，提供了大量的客製空間，網頁做的到的事情他都可以做的到，可以說是功能十分強大。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 960px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 53.06406685236769%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/723a739379011c19c973baf0a4f6ce14/01472/revealjs2.webp 240w,\n/static/723a739379011c19c973baf0a4f6ce14/222bd/revealjs2.webp 480w,\n/static/723a739379011c19c973baf0a4f6ce14/620b9/revealjs2.webp 960w,\n/static/723a739379011c19c973baf0a4f6ce14/28063/revealjs2.webp 1440w,\n/static/723a739379011c19c973baf0a4f6ce14/34ef4/revealjs2.webp 1920w,\n/static/723a739379011c19c973baf0a4f6ce14/c9a76/revealjs2.webp 2872w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/723a739379011c19c973baf0a4f6ce14/0783d/revealjs2.png 240w,\n/static/723a739379011c19c973baf0a4f6ce14/782f4/revealjs2.png 480w,\n/static/723a739379011c19c973baf0a4f6ce14/f570d/revealjs2.png 960w,\n/static/723a739379011c19c973baf0a4f6ce14/8d0ff/revealjs2.png 1440w,\n/static/723a739379011c19c973baf0a4f6ce14/a987b/revealjs2.png 1920w,\n/static/723a739379011c19c973baf0a4f6ce14/97d83/revealjs2.png 2872w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n          type=\"image/png\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/723a739379011c19c973baf0a4f6ce14/f570d/revealjs2.png\"\n          alt=\"reveal.js photo\"\n          title=\"reveal.js photo\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n    </span></p>\n<p>以 code sharing 的角度來看，Reveal.js 使用 highlight.js 來提供 syntax highlight，所以只要用 Reveal.js 來做投影片就不用擔心 code 沒有上色不好看。</p>\n<p>如果喜歡寫 code，想用 html &#x26; javascript 來控制投影片，可以試試看 Reveal.js。此外 Reveal.js 也有提供類似 google slide 的線上編輯網頁，給不會寫 code 或習慣用 GUI 的使用者，都可以去參考使用看看。</p>","fields":{"slug":"/posts/develop-tool-part1/","tagSlugs":["/tag/develop-tool/","/tag/vs-code/"]},"frontmatter":{"date":"2019-08-19T12:00:00.000Z","description":"簡單介紹一下自己用到或看到覺得好用的開發工具，這篇分享一下 code sharing 的工具","tags":["Develop tool","VSCode"],"title":"開發工具分享 Part 1."}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/posts/develop-tool-part1/"}}}